ction fires and I have to say that it's the easiest method I've ever used personally. I cut a lot out in order to make this less than a minute but from start of friction application to flame was under a minute. I've gotten 48 second flames from bow drill before but it was MUCH more effort. I hope you guys enjoy!

Most Viral Edit: Thank you so much for being interested in this one!!! I really enjoyed making this and if you are interested in seeing more of my stuff please check out our channel: https://www.youtube.com/followthecompassnorth

There will be a hand made (by me) Damascus (layered steel) knife giveaway this summer and I answer every question on every YT video so you can consider me your own personal survival resource!</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/jLvW0cr</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[LiberalViking]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Best excuse ever</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/b5S47ud</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/I6WJEp4.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/b5S47ud</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[TiptronicS]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>It's the little things that count.....</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/jYkuzCT</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/9aEV22n.gif" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/jYkuzCT</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[MissDeeMeanor]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I’m one of the burn pit veterans</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/WE9z2E4</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/ufGD5kx.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/Yhhra4q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>As a Marine Corps veteran who was directly exposed on two of my deployments, this disgusts me. My first deployment  (2008) we had to burn our own pit only 75yds from our living area for trash and human waste, as in I was part of working parties that lit our own pits. On my second deployment (2010-2011) we were only 100yds away. I struggle with constant sinusitis, breathing issues, and it just keeps getting worse.

How can this be a partisan issue? How is this even a question of support? These are rhetorical questions, I know why. But still, I don't understand how someone can look at themselves in the mirror every morning and feel good about voting against. 

Source: https://www.congress.gov/bill/117th-congress/house-bill/3967

Source: https://www.govtrack.us/congress/votes/117-2022/h57

Edit: Damn, Most Viral?  Thank you all so much.  Don't send anything, just vote... please.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/WE9z2E4</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[swc0806]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Price gouging</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/n2NSEsC</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/XufvEv5.png" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>$4.11 is about $5.22 in 2022 dollars.  I am seeing gas at $4.30 in my neighborhood. California current avg, regular = $5.740, premium = $6.068, diesel = $6.290 (from the comments)</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/n2NSEsC</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[yokwe]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>I made it past boards</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/QQlNDR1</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/EjWLv7q.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>After 2 long years of nursing school with enough time to get 1 other degree, an adaptive test that can go anywhere from 75-145 questions, I have done it. Thank you Imgur for all the memes and inspirational posts. I hope everyone has a wonderful time today.</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/QQlNDR1</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[alrightalpaca]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Well that’s pretty badass</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/lLIE4jo</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/HsbESwf.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div><div>https://www.democraticunderground.com/100216480100</div></div>]]></description><guid>https://imgur.com/a/lLIE4jo</guid><dc:creator><![CDATA[PatThaiCM]]></dc:creator></item><item><title>Oh Forrest</title><link>https://imgur.com/gallery/4D8n2EB</link><description><![CDATA[<div><img alt="" src="https://i.imgur.com/txasSXJ.jpg" style="max-width: 90%; height: auto;"></div><div><span></span></div></div>]